      protected <T extends org.apache.geode.cache.GemFireCache> T resolveCache()
      Resolves a GemFireCache by attempting to lookup an existing GemFireCache instance in the JVM, first. If an existing GemFireCache could not be found, then this method proceeds in attempting to create a new GemFireCache instance.
